		"excerpt": "The newest CloudFlare App helps you talk with your customers. SnapEngage is live chat for your website, which helps you \"turn visitors into customers and, ultimately, friends.\" Their words, and well said. SnapEngage is a friendly, effective service, useful both for site owners and for customers.",
